Class Lobby

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP50.Lobby
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class Lobby
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
Lobby class is where the clients are put to play against each other Every lobby has a type (Two or Three players) When the game ends, the lobby is freed and can be reused
